1 名船员落水，2 人已成功获救，9 人仍在紧张搜救中。受灾严重地区房屋倒损较多，已紧急转移安置 3050 人；多处电力设施受损，经连夜组织抢修，部分已恢复供电；树木倒伏、围墙倒塌、车辆受损、热水器掉落等情况较多，正在清理清障。目前，社会秩序平稳，生产生活有序。江苏南通极端灾害天气造成 11 人死亡 因灾受伤 102 人"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-924963e852202dd1c0b4990dd17f145f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "884 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457376709"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkviLwNvgh/MVEAMaCDYzOTE5MTI1IJr7soQGMCk43QxABHIJNDU3Mzc2NzA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1619892855.1539495", "card_id": "Q_457415431", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 177}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "京广高铁部分列车晚点 2 小时以上，具体发生了什么？当事者需要负责任吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "石家庄铁路公安处：大风吹扬地膜致接触网故障 使用者被查获 北京铁路回应：因京广高铁大风影响铁路供电，去往保定以远各站高铁晚点。铁路部门正在抢修，线路将尽快开通，预计晚点 2 小时以上，请旅客稍侯或改签后续列车，掌握上车时间。 2021 年 5 月 1 日，京广高铁因供电系统问题，部分列车晚点 2 小时以上，据北京铁路消息，经铁路部门紧急抢修，各次列车将陆续开车，列车运行正逐步恢复。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ef950fcf4f5de43491d1e99259ac03b_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "847 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457415431"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkviLwNvgh/MVEAMaCDYzOTI3NzU4IOastIQGMBI4hQZABXIJNDU3NDE1NDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1619892855.1544783", "card_id": "Q_457072944", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 237}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价热门国产《灵笼》的终章（上部）？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-7ccc8dd33496004bca347da22240e89d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "633 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/457072944"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkviLwNvgh/MVEAMaCDYzODUxODU3IPCHpoQGMA84zQRABnIJNDU3